5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20AI%20has%20sparked%20fears%20that%20companies%20could%20end%20up%20hiring%20fewer%20staff%20in%20the%20years%20to%20come.%20Last%20month%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Anthropic%2C%20Dario%20Amodei%2C%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Axios%20that%20AI%20may%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ceo-warning-ai-could-eliminate-jobs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewipe%20out%20half%20of%20all%20entry-level%20office%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20Amodei%20said%20he%20expects%20unemployment%20to%20rise%20by%2010%25%20to%2020%25%20over%20the%20next%20one%20to%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20them%20are%20unaware%20that%20this%20is%20about%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20sounds%20crazy%2C%20and%20people%20just%20don't%20believe%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20all%20business%20leaders%20agree%20with%20Amodei's%20dire%20prediction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20chip%20giant%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20reporters%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20VivaTech%202025%20in%20Paris%20this%20week%20that%20Amodei%20was%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20pretty%20much%20disagree%20with%20almost%20everything%20he%20says%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said%20of%20Amodei.%20%26quot%3BHe%20thinks%20AI%20is%20so%20scary%2C%20but%20only%20they%20should%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20said%20that%20while%20some%20jobs%20would%20disappear%2C%20AI%20could%20also%20create%20new%20job%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20I%20think%20AI%20will%20change%20jobs%3F%20It%20will%20change%20everyone's%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20changed%20mine%2C%26quot