p%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cencora.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECencora%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20major%20US%20healthcare%20distributor%20and%20clinic%20operator%2C%20faces%20this%20problem%20daily.%20Its%20teams%20handle%20benefits%20verification%2C%20pharmacy%20services%2C%20and%20specialty%20drug%20management%20%E2%80%94%20tasks%20that%20require%20huge%20volumes%20of%20repetitive%20phone%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20administrative%20phone%20calls%20that%20have%20to%20be%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jeff%20Buck%2C%20Cencora's%20vice%20president%20of%20digital%20solutions.%20Internal%20audits%20show%20benefit%20verification%20calls%20at%20Cencora%20can%20take%20up%20to%2090%20minutes%2C%20and%20call%20volumes%20spike%20tenfold%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuman%20staff%20handled%20every%20call%2C%20but%20as%20demand%20grew%2C%20Buck%20says%20Cencora%20turned%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.infinitus.ai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInfinitus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20San%20Francisco%20startup%20founded%20by%20former%20Google%20engineer%20Ankit%20Jain%2C%20to%20help%20automate%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ankit%20Jain%2C%20Founder%20of%20Infinitus%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6849a0c885e81483682be190%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221638%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAnkit%20Jain%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Infinitus.%3Cp%3EInfinitus%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInfinitus%20develops%20AI%20agents%20to%20handle%20calls%2C%20collect%20information%2C%20and%20flag%20tricky%20cases%20for%20a%20human%20to%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJain%20said%20the%20idea%20came%20after%20seeing%20Google's%20AI%20for%20making%20phone%20calls%20on%20behalf%20of%20users%2C%20called%20Duplex%20voice%20AI%2C%20and%20realizing%20similar%20tech%20could%20tackle%20healthcare's%20chronic%20hold-music%20problem.%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20goes%20into%20healthcare%20to%20wait%20on%20hold%20%E2%80%94%20people%20work%20in%20healthcare%20to%20serve%20patients%2C%26quot%3B%20Jain%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20instead%20of%20staff%20waiting%20down%20the%20line%2C%20Infinitus's%20voice%20agent%2C%20Eva%2C%20helps%20Cencora%20handle%20calls%2C%20ask%20questions%2C%20and%20update%20records%20automatically.%20%26quot%3BEva%20will%20actually%20converse%20with%20the%20payer%20counselor%2C%20changing%20the%20way%20she%20asks%20questions%20based%20on%20how%20the%20payer%20responds%2C%26quot%3B%20Buck%20said.%20If%20something's%20unclear%2C%20he%20added%2C%20Eva%20escalates%20it%20to%20a%20human.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECencora%20says%20oversight%20is%20still%20key%2C%20and%20every%20Eva%20call%20is%20recorded%20and%20spot-checked%20by%20the%20quality%20team.%20Cencora%20said%20Eva%20now%20completes%20as%20many%20calls%20as%20over%20100%20full-time%20staff%20and%20processes%20requests%20four%20times%20as%20fast%20as%20before.%20%26quot%3BOur%20test%20showed%20that%20Eva%20even%20caught%20and%20addressed%20inconsistent%20information%20that%20came%20up%20during%20verification%20calls%2C%26quot%3B%20Buck%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221150%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jeff%20Buck%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20digital%20solutions%20at%20Cencora%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684af5a485e81483682bf839%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJeff%20Buck%20is%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20digital%20solutions%20at%20Cencora%3Cp%3ECencora%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20healthcare%20you%20can't%20hallucinate%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jain%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20agent%20only%20says%20things%20that%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bpre-approved.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202024%20Mayo%20Clinic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS2949761224000415%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereview%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20AI-powered%20documentation%20tools%2C%20including%20voice-to-text%20and%20note%20summarization%2C%20can%20significantly%20cut%20clinicians'%20time%20spent%20on%20paperwork%2C%20freeing%20up%20more%20time%20for%20patient%20care%20and%20reducing%20burnout.%20Some%20studies%20cited%20in%20the%20review%20found%20AI%20assistants%20could%20reduce%20documentation%20time%20by%20up%20to%2070%25%2C%20though%20results%20vary%20by%20setting%20and%20tool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20with%20wins%20like%20Cencora%2C%20Jain%20said%20rolling%20out%20new%20tech%20in%20healthcare%20means%20long%20sales%20cycles%20and%20constant%20return%20on%20investment%20audits.%20%26quot%3BChange%20moves%20slowly%20when%20so%20much%20of%20the%20industry%20still%20runs%20on%20fax%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a29bf9b-a6a0-420f-bc34-4ddfed2c0040%5C%22%3EEverfriends%20and%20Hume%20AI%20add%20empathy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVoice%20AI%20isn't%20just%20freeing%20up%20admin%20time%3B%20it's%20also%20stepping%20in%20to%20offer%20comfort%20and%20companionship%20to%20those%20who%20need%20it%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20entrepreneur%20Daniel%20Hungerford%2C%20the%20potential%20of%20the%20tech%20became%20clear%20after%20his%20father%20died%20and%20his%20mother%20was%20left%20alone.%20%26quot%3BIt%20broke%20my%20heart%20every%20time%20she%20said%2C%20'You're%20the%20only%20person%20I've%20talked%20to%20today%2C'%26quot%3B%20Hungerford%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20inspired%20him%20to%20build%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feverfriends.ai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEverfriends%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20smartphone%20app%20that%20acts%20as%20a%20digital%20companion%20for%20seniors%20and%20people%20with%20dementia.%20%26quot%3BWe%20set%20out%20to%20make%20companions%20that%20are%20ultra-realistic%2C%20compassionate%2C%20empathetic%20digital%20best%20friends%2C%26quot%3B%20Hungerford%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20we%20can%20never%20replace%20human%20contact%2C%20but%20our%20goal%20was%20to%20simulate%20it%20as%20closely%20as%20possible%20for%20those%20gaps%20in%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20build%20a%20companion%20that%20could%20respond%20vocally%20with%20real%20empathy%2C%20Hungerford%20used%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hume.ai%2F%3Fgclid%3DCj0KCQjw0qTCBhCmARIsAAj8C4YzExynIAEKrj9YZq9WFLwWwZPMkWmR8c3DIlp8VE6-TFIvxh_eF2gaAnS6EALw_wcB%26campaignid%3D22291527240%26adgroupid%3D%26gad_source%3D1%26gad_campaignid%3D22301914243%26gbraid%3D0AAAAA-9v-gm6PS6d_BesM-Dqrg1YgGRHX%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHume%20AI%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20New%20York-based%20startup%20led%20by%20Alan%20Cowen%2C%20a%20veteran%20of%20Google%20and%20Meta.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20now%20able%20to%20have%20models%20that%20listen%20as%20well%20as%20they%20speak%2C%26quot%3B%20Cowen%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Alan%20Cowen%20Hume%20CEO%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6849a121f748d8c055f37b5c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222662%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlan%20Cowen%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Hume.%3Cp%3EHume%20AI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHume's%20system%20relies%20on%20millions%20of%20human-labelled%20emotion%20samples%2C%20which%20Hungerford%20says%20helps%20Everfriends%20pick%20up%20on%20a%20user's%20mood%20and%20intent%2C%20and%20respond%20in%20a%20way%20that%20feels%20natural.%20If%20someone%20sounds%20anxious%20or%20sad%2C%20the%20AI%20adapts.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20pop%20onto%20Everfriends%20and%20you%20act%20a%20little%20bit%20down%20today%2C%20it%20knows%20that%20you're%20down%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Hungerford%20said.%20For%20people%20with%20dementia%2C%20it%20slows%20down%20or%20repeats%20itself%20as%20needed%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223002%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hume%20AI%20interface%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68498cb5f748d8c055f37869%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221506%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHume's%20empathetic%20voice%20AI%20model.%3Cp%3EHume%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHungerford%20said%20hundreds%20of%20people%20have%20used%20Everfriends%20so%20far.%20Families%2C%20he%20said%2C%20say%20it%20helps%20loved%20ones%20feel%20connected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202025%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F39222000%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereview%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%2013%20studies%20found%20that%20about%2085%25%20of%20studies%20reported%20reduced%20loneliness%20in%20older%20adults%20who%20used%20voice%20assistants%2C%20particularly%20when%20the%20devices%20were%20personalised%20and%20users%20were%20given%20support%20to%20get%20started.%20The%20authors%20said%2C%20however%2C%20that%20more%20research%20and%20larger%2C%20more%20diverse%20samples%20were%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225ef30a42-4907-45de-81a9-682805499aaa%5C%22%3EWhy%20voice%20AI%20still%20needs%20humans%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20founder%20agreed%20that%20voice%20AI%20isn't%20a%20silver%20bullet.%20There%20are%20technical%20and%20social%20limits%2C%20from%20speech%20errors%20and%20background%20noise%20to%20privacy%20and%20digital%20exclusion%2C%20especially%20for%20older%20users%20or%20those%20with%20strong%20accents%20or%20cognitive%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJain%20said%20trust%20and%20transparency%20are%20essential.%20%26quot%3BThe%20voice%20agent%20should%20say%2C%20'I%20can't%20do%20it%2C%20so%20let%20me%20find%20you%20another%20AI%20agent%20or%20a%20human%20agent%20that%20can%20take%20it.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20voice%20AI%20isn't%20a%20substitute%20for%20human%20connection%20or%20oversight%2C%20but%20it%20can%20be%20a%20powerful%20complement.%20The%20founders%20all%20said%20their%20technology%20is%20designed%20to%20support%2C%20not%20rep