D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-succeed-in-school-first-generation-college-student-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20in%20my%20immediate%20family%20to%20graduate%20from%20high%20school%20and%20college%3C%2Fa%3E%20meant%20my%20name%20%E2%80%94%20our%20name%20%E2%80%94%20was%20featured%20proudly%20in%20the%20program%20they%20handed%20out%20at%20graduation.%20My%20father%20had%20framed%20one%20in%20a%20beautiful%20plaque%20that%20hangs%20proudly%20in%20my%20home%20office%2C%20so%20when%20it%20came%20time%20to%20get%20married%2C%20I%20knew%20what%20I%20had%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChanging%20my%20name%20almost%20seemed%20too%20simple.%20I%20filled%20out%20my%20marriage%20certificate%20and%20carefully%20wrote%20Guida-Richards%2C%20a%20tie%20to%20my%20old%20and%20new%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I%20knew%20each%20change%20in%20documents%20and%20credit%20cards%20could%20add%20up%20to%20quite%20a%20few%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20expect%20everyday%20activities%20to%20become%20a%20lot%20more%20difficult%20due%20to%20the%20simple%20addition%20of%20a%20little%20hyphen%20and%20my%20husband's%20last%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220c8d66d3-79cf-4cbe-a5f5-558ce8ccb372%5C%22%3EThe%20hyphen%20became%20a%20headache%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20would%20go%20to%20the%20pharmacy%20to%20pick%20up%20medication%2C%20suddenly%2C%20there%20were%20difficulties%20in%20finding%20me%20in%20the%20system.%20Due%20to%20the%20hyphenated%20name%2C%20locating%20me%20in%20the%20system%20was%20now%20a%20challenge.%20And%20when%20you%20must%20pick%20up%20multiple%20medications%20throughout%20the%20month%20to%20manage%20your%20chronic%20illnesses%2C%20each%20of%20these%20interactions%20starts%20to%20add%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20I%20questioned%20my%20decision%20every%20single%20time%20an%20issue%20arose%3Cem%3E.%20While%20it%20is%3C%2Fem%3E%20completely%20legal%20to%20add%20a%20hyphen%20to%20your%20name%2C%20it%20does