se%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKlarna%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20all%20in%20on%20AI%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20it%20made%20a%20chatbot%20of%20its%20CEO%20to%20take%20customer%20service%20calls.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20AI%20said%20it%20handles%20routine%20queries%2C%20freeing%20up%20human%20workers%20to%20focus%20on%20complex%20issues.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20called%20up%20the%20chatbot%20to%20pick%20its%20artificial%20brain%20about%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fklarna-ceo-ai-may-cause-recession-white-collar-jobs-threat-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKlarna's%20CEO%2C%20Sebastian%20Siemiatkowski%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20believes%20artificial%20intelligence%20is%20capable%20of%20doing%20all%20our%20jobs.%20His%20new%20chatbot%20is%20more%20reserved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fklarna-ipo-employees-in-limbo-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESwedish%20fintech%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20known%20for%20its%20buy%20now%2C%20pay%20later%20service%2C%20created%20an%20AI%20version%20of%20Siemiatkowski%20that%20customers%20can%20call%20for%20support.%20The%20hotline%20launched%20on%20Thursday%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Sweden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20called%20the%20US%20number%20and%20spoke%20to%20the%20chatbot.%20It%20helped%20me%20learn%20more%20about%20purchasing%20power%2C%20expanded%20on%20some%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fklarna-smaller-workforce-ai-boost-revenue-productivity-cost-savings-ipo-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESiemiantkowski's%20views%20on%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20shared%20a%20more%20modest%20take%20on%20AI's%20role%20in%20the%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESiemiatkowski%20has%20been%20a%20vocal%20proponent%20of%20AI%2C%20and%20Klarna%20is%20openly%20experimenting%20with%20the%20technology.%20The%20company%20said%2096%25%20of%20employees%20use%20AI%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fklarna-ceo-sebastian-siemiatkowski-ai-job-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20is%20capable%20of%20doing%20all%20our%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20my%20own%20included%2C%26quot%3B%20because%20it%20now%20has%20reasoning%20capabilities%2C%20Siemiatkowski%20said%20in%20a%20January%20X%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fklarnaseb%2Fstatus%2F1876093526280171699%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20explained%3A%20%26quot%3BOur%20work%20is%20simply%20reasoning%20combined%20with%20knowledge%2Fexperience.%20And%20the%20most%20critical%20breakthrough%2C%20reasoning%2C%20is%20behind%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20Siemiatkowski%20used%20an%20AI%20doppelganger%20to%20deliver%20Klarna's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fklarna-buy-now-pay-later-ai-ceo-sebastian-siemiatkowski-earnings-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Equarterly%20earnings%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20also%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20that%20Klarna's%20%26quot%3BAI-first%20strategy%26quot%3B%20is%20driving%20returns.%20For%20example%2C%20AI%20is%20helping%20increase%20revenue%20per%20employee%2C%20%26quot%3Bslashing%20costs%20across%20the%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20scaling%20up%20its%20merchant%20network%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Siemiatkowski's%20AI%20chatbot%20said%20there%20are%20some%20jobs%20that%20AI%20can't%20replace%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20think%20AI%20will%20completely%20replace%20humans%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20Siemiatkowski%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENo%2C%20I%20don't%20believe%20AI%20will%20completely%20replace%20human%20customer%20service%20at%20Klarna.%20While%20our%20AI%20handles%20about%20two-thirds%20of%20our%20customer%20interactions%2C%20providing%20quick%20solutions%20to%20routine%20queries%2C%20this%20actually%20allows%20our%20human%20teams%20to%20focus%20on%20more%20complex%20issues%20that%20require%20empathy%20and%20a%20deeper%20understanding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWe%20believe%20the%20best%20experience%20comes%20from%20combining%20AI%20efficiency%20with%20genuine%20human%20connection.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bot%20wouldn't%20elaborate%20on%20exactly%20which%20jobs%20Klarna%20would%20continue%20to%20use%20humans%20for.%20It%20reiterated%20that%20AI%20is%20helpful%2C%20but%20Klarna%20still%20needs%20a%20human%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202024%2C%20Klarna%20said%20that%20its%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAI%20customer%20service%20agents%20could%20do%20work%20equivalent%20to%20that%20of%20700%20full-time%20human%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESiemiatkowski%20(the%20human)%20said%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BGrit%26quot%3B%20podcast%20in%20October%20that%20Klarna%20largely%20%26quot%3Bstopped%20hiring%20due%20to%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20it's%20continued%20to%20hire%20some%20engineers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20AI%20will%20lead%20to%20more%20job%20losses%2C%20Siemiatkowski's%20AI%20said%20it's%20a%20question%20may%20people%20are%20thinking%20about%20at%20Klarna%20and%20more%20broadly%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20this%20speed%20of%20AI%20mean%20that%20workers%20lose%20their%20jobs%2C%20or%20at%20least%20some%20workers%20would%20lose%20their%20jobs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20Siemiatkowski%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat's%20a%20really%20important%20question%2C%20and%20it's%20something%20many%20people%20are%20thinking%20about.%20At%20Klarna%20we%20see%20AI%20as%20a%20tool%20that%20helps%20us%20work%20smarter%2C%20not%20necessarily%20as%20something%20that%20replaces%20people%20entirely.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EOur%20goal%20is%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20handle%20the%20more%20routine%20tasks%2C%20which%20then%20frees%20up%20our%20human%20teams%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20more%20complex%20issues%20that%20truly%20require%20empathy%20and%20a%20deeper%20understanding.%20This%20actually%20makes%20their%20work%20more%20rewarding%20and%20allows%20them%20to%20provide%20a%20higher%20quality%20of%20service.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EMore%20broadly%2C%20AI%20will%20certainly%20transform%20society%2C%20and%20it's%20crucial%20that%20we%20as%20a%20society%20think%20about%20how%20to%20support%20people%20through%20these%20changes.%20It's%20about%20thoughtful%20progress%2C%20embracing%20innovation%20while%20also%20ensuring%20we%20support%20everyone%20along%20the%20way%20like.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20Siemiatkowski%20seems%20to%20have%20gotten%20media%20training%20because%20it%20stuck%20to%20the%20topic%20of%20Klarna%20and%20Klarna%20only.%20I%20asked%20what%20it%20thinks%20about%20the%20Trump%20administration%20and%20rival%20payment%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20understand%20your%20point%2C%20but%20my%20focus%20is%20strictly%20on%20Klarna's%20products%20and%20gathering%20customer%20feedback%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bot%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20here%20to%20hear%20about%20your%20experiences%20with%20Klarna%20and%20how%20we%20can%20make%20things%20even%20better%20for%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFair%20point%2C%20AI%20Siemiatkowski.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fklarna-ceo-chatbot-answers-questions-about-ai-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749760720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F684b01973d5881a51c1b4b0d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fklarna-ceo-chatbot-answers-questions-about-ai-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20asked%20an%20AI%20chatbot%20based%20on%20Klarna's%20CEO%20to%20share%20its%20views%20on%20artificial%20intelligence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhart%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Hart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A43%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com