C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERep.%20Mark%20Pocan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpocan.house.gov%2Fsites%2Fevo-subsites%2Fpocan.house.gov%2Ffiles%2Fevo-media-document%2Fnoise-mitigation-letter-pdf.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esent%20a%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Office%20of%20Local%20Defense%20Community%20Cooperation%2C%20a%20DC-based%20agency%20within%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20that%20helps%20military%20bases%20work%20with%20their%20local%20communities%2C%20after%20the%20group%20denied%20funding%20for%20noise%20mitigation%20efforts%20for%20some%20Madison%20citizens%2C%20who%20Pocan%20says%20are%20plagued%20by%20the%20jet's%20deafening%20Pratt%20%26amp%3B%20Whitney%20engines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETruax%20Field%20Air%20National%20Guard%20Base%2C%20which%20is%20home%20to%20the%20115th%20Fighter%20Wing%20and%20its%20F-35A%20Lighting%20II%20Joint%20Strike%20Fighters%2C%20is%20located%20in%20Madison%2C%20Wisconsin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Office%20of%20Local%20Defense%20Community%20Cooperation%20has%20funded%20DoD%20noise-mitigation%20efforts%20and%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Foldcc.gov%2Four-programs%2Fcommunity-noise-mitigation-program%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20an%20entire%20office%20dedicated%20to%20handling%20community%20noise%20issues%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20military%20fixed-wing%20aviation.%20The%20office%20offered%20Madison%20residents%20%2450%20million%20in%20fiscal%20year%202021%2C%20according%20to%20Pocan's%20letter%2C%20%26quot%3Bto%20make%20necessary%20modifications%20to%20their%20homes%20to%20dampen%20the%20noise%20and%20improve%20their%20quality%20of%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20similar%20request%2C%20however%2C%20for%20%2418%20million%20for%20other%20Madison%20residents%20was%20nixed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPocan%20said%20in%20his%20letter%20that%20%26quot%3Bthis%20effort%20would%20have%20allowed%20for%20better%20insulation%20in%20over%20160%20homes%20to%20help%20cushion%20the%20noise%2C%20as%20well%20as%20new%20windows%20or%20HVAC%20systems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202012%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthvermont.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fdocuments%2F2016%2F11%2FEIS_F-35A_Jets%25202012.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVermont%20Health%20Department%3C%2Fa%3E%20study%20found%20that%20F-35%20jets%20reached%20a%20peak%20noise%20level%20of%20115%20decibels%2C%20or%20approximately%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hearingconservation.org%2Fassets%2FDecibel.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esame%20noise%20level%20as%20a%20rock%20concert%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20louder%20than%20the%20F-16s%20the%20115th%20Fighter%20Wing%20previously%20flew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20the%20decision%20to%20place%20F-35%20fighter%20jets%20at%20Truax%20Field%20in%202020%2C%20my%20office%20has%20repeatedly%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20to%20express%20my%20concerns%20about%20what%20impact%20the%20noise%20from%20these%20jets%20could%20have%20on%20local%20residents%2C%20their%20homes%2C%20and%20local%20businesses%2C%26quot%3B%20Pocan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20years%20since%2C%20residents%20have%20reported%20consistent%20and%20significant%20concerns%20with%20the%20noise%20levels%20to%20my%20office%2C%20along%20with%20fears%20that%20prolonged%20exposure%20could%20lead%20to%20property%20damage%20or%20negative%20health%20impacts%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20congressman%20requested%20that%20the%20office%20send%20an%20official%20out%20to%20Madison%20to%20explain%20its%20rejection%20to%20the%20community%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Office%20of%20Local%20Defense%20Community%20Cooperation%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20its%20planned%20response%20to%20Pocan's%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20noisy%20jets%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmadison365.com%2Fmadison-residents-still-negatively-impacted-by-arrival-of-f-35-fighter-jets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20made%20headlines%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Wisconsin%2C%20where%20residents%20near%20the%20Truax%20Field%20Air%20National%20Guard%20Base%20have%20had%20to%20contend%20with%20the%20aircraft%20regularly%20since%20their%20arrival%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EF-35s%20have%20also%20riled%20up%20other%20residents%20across%20the%20country%20where%20the%20advanced%20fighter%20jets%20are%20housed%2C%20disturbing%20residents%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkutv.com%2Fnews%2F2news-investigates%2Fneighbors-of-hill-air-force-base-desperate-for-solutions-to-destructive-jet-noise-safe-skies-utah-noise-concerns-f-35-jets-military-study-conducted%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUtah%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.azpm.org%2Fp%2Fenvironmentnews%2F2020%2F3%2F11%2F167457-opponents-speak-out-at-hearing-on-bringing-f-35-fighter-jet-to-tucson%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMost%2520of%2520the%2520public%2520complaints%2C10%2520is%2520already%2520too%2520loud.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArizona%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Vermont%2C%20where%20some%20people%20have%20even%20reported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvtdigger.org%2F2020%2F09%2F27%2Fpanic-attacks-ringing-ears-shaking-walls-happy-1-year-anniversary-to-the-f-35s%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epanic%20attack-like%20symptoms%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwisconsin-lawmaker-pushes-f-35-noise-relief-new-noise-complaint-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749757129000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwisconsin-lawmaker-pushes-f-35-noise-relief-new-noise-complaint-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Wisconsin%20lawmaker%20is%20frustrated%20with%20how%20loud%20the%20F-35s%20flying%20out%20of%20Truax%