urselves.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20unWOOD%20became%20a%20brand%20of%20outdoor%20furniture.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESo%2C%20how%20exactly%20does%20unWOOD%20turn%20trash%20into%20treasure%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20It%20starts%20with%20the%20waste%20no%20one%20wants%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20cities%2C%20Material%20Recovery%20Facilities%20(MRFs)%2C%20clean%20plastic%20goes%20to%20regular%20recyclers%20but%20the%20soiled%2C%20mixed%2C%20and%20multilayered%20plastic%20usually%20gets%20tossed%20aside.%20That%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20the%20kind%20of%20trash%20unWOOD%20picks%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T163444.915-1749639904.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22benches%20from%20unWOOD%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T163444.915-1749639904.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T163444.915-1749639904-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T163444.915-1749639904-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T163444.915-1749639904-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-11T163444.915-1749639904-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-447769%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBenches%20made%20out%20of%20unWOOD%20are%20durable%20and%20are%20perfect%20for%20outdoors.%3C%2Ff