mers%20establish%20their%20ventures%2C%20Dinil%20created%20employment%20opportunities%20and%20promoted%20sustainable%20practices%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArpit%20Byju%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20Pookkad%2C%20Kozhikode%2C%20was%20interested%20in%20cage%20fishing.%20With%20Dinil%E2%80%99s%20help%2C%20he%20started%20fish%20farming%20in%20two%20cages.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20immense%20scope%20in%20caged%20fish%20farming.%20Usually%2C%20feed%20waste%20creates%20ammonia%20in%20the%20pond%2C%20but%20because%20this%20setup%20is%20in%20flowing%20river%20water%2C%20there%20is%20no%20stagnant%20waste.%20You%20only%20need%20a%20little%20area%20to%20do%20this.%20I%20started%20with%20two%20and%20now%20wish%20to%20increase%20it%20to%20eight%20cages%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arpit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDinil%20helped%20me%20in%20everything%20from%20paperwork%20to%20the%20setup%2C%20and%20gave%20me%20fish%20babies.%20He%20charged%20only%20Rs%2010%2C000%20for%20the%20setup.%20I%20admire%20Dinil%20for%20his%20dedication.%20He%20spent%20so%20many%20years%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20his%20decision%20to%20switch%20careers%20is%20commendable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECage%20fish%20farming%3A%20An%20overview%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDinil%20explains%20that%20caged%20fish%20farming%20is%20a%20method%20of%20cultivating%20fish%20in%20a%20controlled%20environment.%20This%20involves%20placing%20fish%20in%20cages%20or%20enclosures%20that%20are%20submerged%20in%20natural%20water%20bodies%20such%20as%20rivers%2C%20lakes%2C%20or%20seas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cages%20allow%20water%20to%20flow%20freely%20through%20them%2C%20providing%20a%20steady%20supply%20of%20oxygen%20and%20nutrients%20to%20the%20fish%20while%20containing%20them%20within%20a%20defined%20area.%20This%20farming%20system%20mimics%20fish%E2%80%99s%20natural%20habitat%20but%20allows%20for%20greater%20control%20over%20the%20environment%20and%20pro